{"type": "article", "id": 8991, "title": "McDonald X Colette 时尚单品", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-29T07:34:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234950y49Cmed1zYSuh3lB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tMcDonald 最近和巴黎流行时尚店 Colette 联名推出了一系列时尚单品，有 T 恤，包袋，明信片，围巾，手机壳，笔记本等，这些作品上的图案都是来自于去年 TBWA 为麦当劳做的海报竞选活动，基本上以像素画为主。本次售卖时间从 5 月 4 号开始，会一直持续到月底。不过，目前在价格上我们还没有准确信息。这是<a href=\"http://www.colette.fr/\" target=\"_blank\"> Colette 官方网站</a>，感兴趣的话可以保持关注。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234947OFLjhKE7GpXzRVQk.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.664\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234947BUHXiDjvpAYwQ40R.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.664\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234948K5gzDX6jeHfnNlFx.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.69637883\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523494806SlwnO29mVYe1Xa.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.43266476\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234949Gv8XO1WAxIp7fJqg.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.664\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234949XUCtAWOaLESG4HQ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}